Subject: [PATCH] clk: rockchip: fix i2s gate bits on rk3066 and rk3188

The Rockchip PX2/RK3066 uses these bits in CRU_CLKGATE7_CON:

hclk_i2s_8ch_gate_en  bit 4 (dtsi: i2s0)
hclk_i2s0_2ch_gate_en bit 2 (dtsi: i2s1)
